headline: Halliburton: Large And Steady Player In Energy Services

headline: TechnipFMC's Q1 Earnings & Revenues Miss Estimates, Rise Y/Y
summary: FTI expects revenues in the range of $8.4-$8.8 billion and $1.2-$1.35 billion for the Subsea and Surface Technologies unit, respectively, for 2025.
